        class="w-full lg:w-[590px]
      h-[260px] sm:h-[500px] md:h-[650px] lg:h-[559px]
      rounded-[30px] overflow-hidden flex-shrink-0"
      >
        <img
          src={martinaImg.src}
          alt="Martina Murphy"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        />
      </div>

      <!-- TEXT -->
      <div
        class="w-full lg:w-[590px]
      flex flex-col items-start
      px-0 lg:pl-[60px]
      pt-6 lg:pt-[60px]
      pb-6 lg:pb-[80px]
      gap-8 lg:gap-10"
      >
        <div class="w-full flex flex-col gap-8 lg:gap-10">
          <!-- TITLE -->
          <h2
            class="font-['Crimson_Text'] font-normal
          text-black tracking-[-0.03em]
          text-[34px] sm:text-[44px] md:text-[54px] lg:text-[60px]
          leading-[95%]"
          >
            Hello, I’m Martina
          </h2>

          <!-- DESCRIPTION -->
          <p
            class="font-['DM_Sans'] font-normal
          text-[#6F6F6F] tracking-[-0.005em]
          text-[16px] sm:text-[18px] lg:text-[21px]
          leading-[150%]"
          >
            And I own Martina Murphy Solicitors, I’m here along with my partners
            to fully support you in whatever it is that you need. I guarantee
            that you will feel comfortable, welcome and respected.

            <br /><br />

            We are one of the few practices in the Mid-West to have been awarded
            the LQ Standard of Excellence – an independent verification of the
            standard of care we give to all our clients.

            <br /><br />

            Our clients return time and time again when they need legal advice
            and most importantly, they are happy to refer family and friends to
            the office.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

